<br>
I think it's a great idea. First, because of the predictability of the Nexus, portal camping would be horrendous, and second because, I think disabling PvP in the Bazaar will greatly increase cross-trading (which I have no problem with... I don't mind selling to the enemy if I can make some extra plat ^_^).<br>
